ct their doctor if it occurs. Patients should be observed for loss of glycemic control when these drugs are withdrawn.', 'Synergism', 'Close monitoring for the development of hypoglycemia is recommended if these drugs are coadministered with insulin secretagogues, particularly in patients with advanced age and/or renal impairment.', NULL, NULL, 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic');
